Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ANY TIME, ANY WHERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever and wherever you go, bring along a Nijimura bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spilled water on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bumped into something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ANY TIME, ANY WHERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever and wherever you need a bag, get Nijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,ANYTIME, ANYWHERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:26.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Whenever and wherever you go, bring along a Nijimura bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are Nijimura bags really selling hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's their rainbow color trademark that makes them so popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Nijimura bags are very sturdy, and they're highly waterproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the fastener - it's said to be the\Nsame kind they use for scuba diving suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the contents won't get wet\Neven when the bag's dropped in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, no doubt this is a celebrity\Nbrand - there's one too many zeroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, two more than our budget!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd hoped to find a pouch inside our budget\Nrange, but I guess I'll have to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've taken on President Nijimura's personal request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we accomplish this, be it a pouch or\Na poncho, I'll buy anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't carry ponchos you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for your wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Nijimura should be available in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Nijimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, bu sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hidden in the rainbow colors after the rain is a handbag's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had roadblocks set up five minutes after the incident\Noccurred, but have failed to locate any suspicious vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you misread the plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, you are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:20.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Inspector Katsuragi from SID, Detective Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:20.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi Kenzou (45)\NPolice HQ First Division Special Investigation Dept. Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SID?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First division of the police headquarters,\Nthe Special Investigation Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a section for handling hostage situations\Nsuch as kidnappings or hijackings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, why is a kid like you in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also witnessed the crime scene, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us if we are interfering with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective, may I ask you to stay away from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigating kidnappings for ransom is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't be sure that this case's kidnapping is for ransom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:03.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(210,00)\3c&H5B2227&}Nijimura Saki (35)\NNijimura Vice President
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This was inside our mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Nijimura's wife, my name is Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am the vice president of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We have President Nijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want him released, put Â¥ 100,000,000\Nin a Nijimura handbag and have Saki carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"At precisely 14:00, go to Touto-Ikebukuro\NStation and board the Blue Sky express train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Have her get off at the last stop - Okuho Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"However, ANYTIME ANYWHERE, we will be watching closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If we see any authorities, the hostage will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Black Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hundred million yen ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any idea who they might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, we've always had problems\Nwith counterfeit products copying our brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have just begun filing a lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that those types of companies\Nwould hold a grudge because of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's plausible, since that "ANYTIME AYNWHERE"\Nin the ransom note is Nijimura's catch phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, adding "black" in front of your rainbow trademark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something a counterfeit company would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will take over the investigation, so leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was actually contacted by my husband\Nto collect evidence pertaining to the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm also afraid to carry that much money all by\Nmyself, so I'd like him to be my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to carry it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Touto Ikebukuro Station Inbound
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Express Train Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, why do you guys have to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As camouflage, didn't you say so yourself, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Hiking, hiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anytime, anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know when or where the culprit may appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:11.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next stop is the final stop, Okuho Station. Okuho Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You may transfer to the Koushuu Express Line or the Touto Okuho Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:20.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Okuho Station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, what did the culprit say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Transfer now."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be late for the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We barely made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would've taken forever to wait for the next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see that paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:58.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,TRANSFER TO THE\NTOUTO - OKUHO LINE,\NAND WHEN YOU REACH\NTHE MIDDLE OF THE\NNAKATORO BRIDGE,\NTOSS THE RANSOM\NMONEY BAG!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Transfer to the Touto-Okuho Line, and when you reach the\Nmiddle of the Nakatoro Bridge, toss the ransom money bag."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:09:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nakatoro Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What siren is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad, the dam's discharging!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's plan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To flush away the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's why they demanded the money be\Nput in a sturdy and waterproof Nijimura bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, what a cunning criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact the other squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Downstream! Have them go downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your husband is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this â\hwhat's eating at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have this terrible feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still can't locate the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Continue the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our transmitter bug planted on the name tag\Nseems to have been damaged by the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, my terrible feeling soon ended up true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The handbag, swept away by the dam discharge, was\Nrecovered at the riverbank 5 kilometers downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the hundred million yen inside the\Nbag was apparently taken by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to wait for the release of the hostage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next morning, along with the stolen\Nvehicle that was used during the kidnapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Nijimura's murdered body was also found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darling, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will do everything we can to apprehend the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like hell you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because they spotted you police that they killed my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't expose ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was you! You were discovered by the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of "great detective" are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding your husband's murder,\Nwe've come across new information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of Nijimura's murder was determined\Nto be between 11:00 AM and noon yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was kidnapped around 10:30 AM, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They think hostages only hinder them, so they\Nkilled him shortly after the kidnapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And still worked up the nerve to demand a ransom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, why's that kid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name tag with the bug is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brats need to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, our culprit is a ruthless murderer and sly as a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we will be joining the investigation from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although at a time like this, no, because of a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:53.48,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Madam Saki Takes\NPresident's Place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to respond to the love and support shown to our Nijimura bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hereby vow to work hard to live up the reputation of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, regarding the counterfeit products that have\Nbeen causing problems to my beloved customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will request that law enforcement authorities enhance\Ntheir effort in fighting copyright infringement...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until total annihilation has been achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Recheck crime scenes thoroughly," it's the\Nmotto of the police, no, for detectives too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I work when a kid's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I was at the scene from the beginning this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Uncle forgets or misses something, I might be able to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare talk back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, two heads are better than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three heads are better than two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the scene from the beginning too,\Nso I can't allow you to leave me by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nimura Office Backdoor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incident started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How scary, to think the kidnapping happened right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police set up roadblocks immediately,\Nyet still failed to spot the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carrying the ransom money, Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nboarded the Blue Sky express train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Okuho Station
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She then got off here - at Okuho Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, this was the culprit's attempt to distract the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as the train she transfered to\Nwas just about to pass the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She tossed the bag into the river from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was when the dam was scheduled to discharge water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, the bag was swept away by the rising water level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it was finally found at the riverbank 5 kilometers downstream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ransom money had already been taken by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, the name tag that was fitted with the\Ntransmitter bug wasn't found with the bag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bag tumbled downstream due to the force of the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tag must've fallen off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, the discharge was surprisingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think it could have pushed a bag weighing\N10 kilograms over a distance of five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must've been carrying a lot of weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to carry it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Nijimura speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured out who killed your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That press conference of yours served as a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, I will reveal the truth at the\Nriverbank under the bridge where the bag was tossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under that bridge, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, for the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's... the ransom money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't the bag swept away...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain this to us, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who wants to ask that, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bag we found downstream was a dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you toss the bag into a dam discharge, people\Nwould think it'd get washed away downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was your diversionary tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, try emptying the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bag... why is it so heavy even when it's empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An iron plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the metal weight planted inside,\Nthe bag stayed under the bridge until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have been fooled by the culprit into believing the\Ndummy bag at the downstream riverbank was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've panicked when you heard that\NI'd reveal the truth here tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, you came to quickly collect the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the bag - that would've otherwise been unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't want us to find out that the bag downstream,\Nunlike the bag with ransom money in it, was a counterfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A counterfeit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bag was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although they look alike...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fake bag has a slightly different\Ncolor arrangement than the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this kidnapping case, there was an\Nunnatural situation I'd like to address.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is, the culprit didn't restrain the hostage,\Nbut merely seated him in the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the kidnapping was\Nactually staged by Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Nijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wanted none other than me,\NMouri Kogorou, to become a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the reason why the kidnapper's car\Nwasn't caught in your timely roadblock...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because they hid themselves\Nin a parking garage near the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But immediately after that, you killed Nijimura in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest would be simply your solo play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mailed yourself the ransom note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you prepared the kidnapper's instructions\Nyourself while among the crowd of passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made it look like the culprit was really there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Saki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why did you use a counterfeit bag as your dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had you used a real bag, perhaps your\Nplan would've never been seen through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could do that, now could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nijimura's products are like my adorable children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I'd damage my own bag like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something I could never do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you used a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it was all the counterfeit company's\Nfault that our household income was suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite this, that man cut a deal with the counterfeit\Ncompany, getting dirty money from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then put everything into gambling and went deeply in debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he came up with this staged\Nkidnapping idea to pay off his debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I pretended to agree and took him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brand is the result of my design and all my hard work, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ANYTIME, ANYWHERE...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was her handmade bag, be it submerged into\Nthe water or withstanding the dam discharge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would definitely protect the 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Betting on her confidence and pride, she committed the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lost her gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rainbow across the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a leg across my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an organization I must crush,\Neven if it requires sacrificing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were here, we wouldn't have to fear that Bourbon guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't fear him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, Akai Shuuichi is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bank robbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.03,0:24:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eye covering
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:54.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the Next Episode
